\section{Conclusion}
This report provides a single-column, presentation-oriented submission artifact that combines
system diagrams and dashboard evidence with explicit interpretation. The structure is intentionally
reviewer-friendly: architecture first, then five dashboard pages, then conclusion. The same flow also
works as a live presentation script.

